        "text_KHmP9L": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Choosing the right vaporizer is not just about specs. It is about finding the experience that fits your lifestyle, your preferences, and the way you like to session.</p><p>This guide covers what really matters before investing in a premium device, from heating technology and build materials to portability, battery life, and long-term maintenance. Whether you are a daily user or upgrading for a better experience, this is the right place to start.</p><p>Among today’s premium options, the <strong>AirVape Legacy PRO 2</strong> and <strong>Legacy CORE </strong>stand out for a reason. Here is what makes them worth your attention.</p>"
          }
