    "collapsible_content_ak87T3": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "block_6MgrKi": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Heating Technology",
            "content": "<p>The<strong> Legacy PRO 2</strong> and <strong>Legacy CORE</strong> both use <strong>hybrid heating</strong>, combining convection and conduction for more even vaporization and smoother flavor.</p><p>This gives you faster sessions, more efficient material use, and better overall temperature performance. It is one of the biggest reasons these devices feel more premium than entry-level options.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_cpYRLP": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Advanced Control vs Essential Experience",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>Legacy PRO 2</strong> is built for users who want maximum control and more premium features. It offers precise temperature adjustment, a full display for key settings, <strong>On-Demand Mode</strong>, and <strong>wireless charging</strong>.</p><p>The <strong>Legacy CORE</strong> is for users who want a more straightforward premium experience. It focuses on the essentials with <strong>7 preset temperature settings</strong> and <strong>USB-C charging</strong>, while also standing out through <strong>vibrant color options</strong> and <strong>interchangeable face skins</strong> for a more personal look.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_Jn3LCz": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Battery + Charging",
            "content": "<p>Battery life plays a huge role in everyday use. The <strong>Legacy PRO 2</strong> and <strong>Legacy CORE</strong> both offer strong battery performance for dependable, longer sessions.<br/><br/>The <strong>PRO 2</strong> goes further with <strong>wireless charging</strong> for added convenience, while the <strong>CORE</strong> keeps things simple and efficient with <strong>USB-C charging</strong>. Both are designed to support regular use without feeling limited.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_BGFX8K": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Airpath + Materials",
            "content": "<p>Premium materials make a real difference in how a vaporizer performs.<br/><br/>The <strong>Legacy PRO 2</strong> and <strong>Legacy CORE</strong> feature an <strong>isolated airpath</strong> with stainless steel and glass to help keep vapor cleaner and cooler. Their <strong>gold-plated heating chambers</strong> support more consistent heat transfer and better flavor integrity without exposed electronics in the vapor path.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_MGEx6R": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Portability + Use",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>PRO 2</strong> and <strong>CORE</strong> strike a strong balance between performance and portability. They are compact enough to travel comfortably, but powerful enough to deliver full sessions at home.<br/><br/>If your top priority is minimal size above everything else, the <strong>XS GO</strong> or <strong>OM Keychain Waxpen</strong> may be a better fit. If you want a more complete premium experience, the <strong>Legacy line</strong> makes more sense.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_DHa4ec": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Cleaning + Maintenance",
            "content": "<p>A device should not feel annoying to own after the first week. That is where design really matters.</p><p>The <strong>Legacy PRO 2</strong> and <strong>Legacy CORE</strong> are built for easier long-term upkeep, with features like a <strong>magnetic chamber lid</strong>, <strong>removable mouthpiece</strong>, and accessible isolated parts that make cleaning simpler and more straightforward.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        }
      },
