      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "subheading": "",
        "heading": "Key Buying Considerations",
        "content": "<p>A premium vaporizer should do more than simply heat your material. It should deliver smoother flavor, better consistency, easier maintenance, and a more refined experience every time you use it.</p><p>These are the key things to look at before choosing the right device.</p>",
