        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"use-chooser\">\n  <h2 class=\"use-chooser__title\">Choose Based on <br> Your Usage</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"use-chooser__row\">\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__need\">Premium daily use and flavor</div>\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__choice\">Legacy PRO 2</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"use-chooser__row\">\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__need\">Simple daily use with personal style</div>\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__choice\">Legacy CORE</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"use-chooser__row\">\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__need\">Light, pocket-sized travel use</div>\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__choice\">XS GO</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"use-chooser__row\">\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__need\">Quick hits and microdosing</div>\n    <div class=\"use-chooser__choice\">OM Keychain WaxPen</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.use-chooser {\n  max-width: 900px;\n  margin: 2rem auto;\n  font-family: inherit;\n}\n.use-chooser__title {\n  text-align: center;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  font-size: 1.6rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n/* rows */\n.use-chooser__row {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; /* 2 columns on desktop */\n  border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.use-chooser__need,\n.use-chooser__choice {\n  padding: 14px 16px;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n.use-chooser__need {\n  background: #f9f9f9;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n.use-chooser__choice {\n  font-weight: 700;\n  background: #fff;\n  color: #111;\n}\n\n/* mobile: stack columns */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .use-chooser__row {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* stack into single column */\n  }\n  .use-chooser__choice {\n    border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
